data.description: Completely updated twin on quiet street in Lansdowne. Perfectly situated to walk to Nile Swim Club and Yeadon Community Park. Nice curb appeal with newer grey siding and large corner lot. Enter into a spacious, natural light filled living room with a stone fireplace, vinyl plank flooring and neutral paint. Same attractive flooring continues into the dining room for easy entertaining and convenient access into the large, bright kitchen.  Kitchen updates include recessed lighting, stainless steel appliances, wood cabinetry and neutral tile backsplash. Mud room off the kitchen gives access to the backyard and two car detached garage, a rare find for this location! New carpet continues upstairs to three generously sized bedrooms as well as a sunny hall bathroom with tub shower combination.  The fourth bedroom is on the finished third floor level.  Additional storage area in the large unfinished basement. Easy commute to Philadelphia and PHL International airport.
